title: Grateful Dead Live at Shoreline Amphitheatre on 1990-06-17
description: Shakedown Street, Little Red Rooster, Jack A Roe, Easy To Love You, Queen Jane Approximately, Bird Song-> Promised Land Iko Iko, Picasso Moon, Ship of Fools, Playin' In The Band-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> Space-> I Will Take You Home-> I Need A Miracle-> Stella Blue-> Throwing Stones-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: The Weight

reviews.review_text: I will take you home w/brents daughter sitting with him A barely passable (for the era) but listenable recording of an underrated Father's Day show on a lazy Sunday afternoon where the Dead stretch out and take their time on a variety of typical yet nicely played songs

My Last Brent Show Little did I know but this would be my last Brent show....I just remember being in the taper section right behind Healy....thinking how lucky we are to be here...Good Recording...
Tho the file info is screwed up due to the misslabled Tunings files...Can Somebody Fix this?

The correct order! Here's the correct order of the songs, so that when you download the MP3s and get the 4 unnamed trackes, you know how to retag...
